          <span class="hideText">Comments</span>
          <span class="fa fa-comments"></span> 
          <span id="echo_container" class="echo_container comment-vars echo-counter text" guid="http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/early-lead/wp/2014/04/26/doc-rivers-son-has-best-response-to-donald-sterlings-comments/"></span>
